text: Diourbel is a region in the central west of Senegal. The regional capital is Diourbel. As of the 2013 census, 1,420,082 people lived there. It has an area of . == Départements == There are three départements: * Bambey Département * Diourbel Département * Mbacké Département Category:Regions of Senegal
